      • autoFiles

        private static java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.String[]> autoFiles
        A HashMap of CSV files for ProfileFollower. Keys are in the form of START+END where START and END are either L or R, for left and right respectively. (i.e. if START and END are both L the key should be LL.)

        Values are string lists representing the location of the appropriate CSV files in the RoboRIO's filesystem.

        public static OI oi
